import { DefaultTheme } from 'react-native-paper'

export const theme = {
  ...DefaultTheme,
  colors: {
    ...DefaultTheme.colors,
    text: '#000000',
    primary: '#560CCE',
    secondary: '#414757',
    error: '#f13a59',
    background: '#E5E5E5',
    link :'#0B6DF1',
    button: '#6DA0E4',
    logo:'#125ABB',
    white:'#fff',
    black: '#000000',
    header : '#88E0EF',
    silver:'#CDCDCD'
  },
}
